  "body": "### Description\r\nAs an operator, I want to keep tabs on which miners sent me solutions, so I may reward them.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Implement an optional configuration flag to allow to register miners with a persistent store.\r\n* The persistent store should record miners identities taken after their username as their address.\r\n* The persistent store should track solutions sent by miners over time.\r\n* Besu should be able to calculate according to 2 different schemes:\r\n** Pay-per-share: every time a miner sends a valid share, it is added to the rewards.\r\n** Pay-per-block: every time a block is submitted and becomes part of the canonical chain thanks to a solution provided by a miner, they get a reward. A smaller reward goes to solutions associated with ommers.\r\n",
